  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I realize that to be alone is not just a-- a-- a simple thing of being alone, but you're missing something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But according to the studies of the people, the whole construction of the of the marriage is to have children and have family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, the children supposed to take care of in the later stages of the parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is not always the fact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's always that sometime that the parents, despite the fact that they are old and in need of the children, has to support the children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or they are so far away that they can't be of any help to them anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I don't know the controversial situation of being married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, I think that perhaps participating in this society, one should be married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It would be of better social value.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in engineering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first job I had with a large breaking concern where machinery was involved, and I was working over there for 22 years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I started to work for K-Mart apparel and with the sophisticated-- sophisticated equipment, where electronic equipment was involved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had my educational background in a technical field from Germany and while I was waiting for my migration to the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the United States attending various schools, among them Brooklyn Polytechnical.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The tragedy of the Holocaust there is, what people are talking about Holocaust they're, minimizing the true value of the word.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Holocaust is not just elimination and destruction of a certain race, group, or ethnic, or religious group.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
